title: STULZ Clima Unit: Temperatures
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/stulz
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This plug-in polls the air temperature of all connected clima units on a stulz management.
 It is possible to define levels for warning and critical temperature. The plug-in return
 {CRIT} or {WARN} if the current temperatue is higher then one of the levels.

item:
 The sensor type (e.g. {{unit air}}), the bus and the unit number, e.g. {{unit return air 2-1}}

discovery:
 One service is created for each device.
